tools.description:
HTTP GET /materials

Optional arguments: authorization, fieldsMaterials, filterIschild, filterManufacturer, filterUpdatedAtGt, filterUpdatedAtLt, include, pageSize, pageNumber, sort

Argument mapping:
• authorization → Authorization (header, optional) e.g. 54748d91aaf019c83c3c66edd2324fbb
• fieldsMaterials → fields[materials] (query, optional) e.g. fields[materials]=materialTags,manufacturer,name,referenceCode,units,unitCost,updatedAt,createdBy,parentMaterial,childMaterialsCount
• filterIschild → filter[isChild] (query, optional) e.g. filter[isChild]=false
• filterManufacturer → filter[manufacturer] (query, optional) e.g. filter[manufacturer]=2
• filterUpdatedAtGt → filter[updated_at][gt] (query, optional) e.g. filter[updated_at][gt]=2025-01-13 10:00:00
• filterUpdatedAtLt → filter[updated_at][lt] (query, optional) e.g. filter[updated_at][lt]=2025-01-13 10:00:00
• include → include (query, optional) e.g. include=materialTags,manufacturer,createdBy,parentMaterial
• pageSize → page[size] (query, optional) e.g. page[size]=25
• pageNumber → page[number] (query, optional) e.g. page[number]=2
• sort → sort (query, optional) e.g. name

