tools.description:
HTTP PATCH /opportunities/{OPPORTUNITY_ID}

Required arguments: opportunityId

Optional arguments: fieldsProductions, fieldsCompanies, fieldsDocuments, fieldsEmployees, fieldsProfiles, fieldsBuildingdivisions, fieldsProperties, fieldsPrimaryproposal, include, body

Argument mapping:
• opportunityId → OPPORTUNITY_ID (path, required)
• fieldsProductions → fields[productions] (query, optional) e.g. fields[productions]=type,opportunityType,propertyId,domain,name,namePrefix,nameNumber,description,propertyName,cost,price,dueDate,dueAt,dueDateHasTime,projectedCloseDate,options,custom,archivedAt,forecastedAt,heldAt,latestStageTransitionedAt,estimateTotals,estimatedStartDate,leadOpenedAt,leadPendingAt,leadQuotedAt,leadSoldAt,leadDeadAt,openedAt,scheduledAt,startedAt,completedAt,invoicedAt,closedAt,status,displayStatus,biddingCompanies,billedCompany,contacts,contacts.image,createdBy,estimator,leadType,primaryProposal,productionItems,profile,property,availableTransitions,productionStageTransitions,workflow,workflowStage,relatedProductions,divisions,siteBidDocuments
