tools.description:
HTTP GET /productions/{PRODUCTION_ID}

Required arguments: productionId

Optional arguments: authorization, fieldsCompanies, fieldsEmployees, fieldsProfiles, fieldsProductiondays, fieldsProperties, include

Argument mapping:
• authorization → Authorization (header, optional) e.g. 54748d91aaf019c83c3c66edd2324fbb
• productionId → PRODUCTION_ID (path, required)
• fieldsCompanies → fields[companies] (query, optional) e.g. fields[companies]=name,type,options
• fieldsEmployees → fields[employees] (query, optional) e.g. fields[employees]=name
• fieldsProfiles → fields[profiles] (query, optional) e.g. fields[profiles]=name
• fieldsProductiondays → fields[productionDays] (query, optional) e.g. fields[productionDays]=id
• fieldsProperties → fields[properties] (query, optional) e.g. fields[properties]=name,company,options,primaryBuildingId
• include → include (query, optional) e.g. include=availableTransitions,availableTransitions.fromStage,availableTransitions.toStage,productionStageTransitions,productionStageTransitions.toStage,productionStageTransitions.toStage.workflow,productionStageTransitions.transitionedBy,workflow,workflowStage,billedCompany,contractorCompany,createdBy,days,managers,property,property.company,workProfile,contacts,contacts.image,relatedProductions,divisions,divisions.productTemplateTag

