tools.description:
HTTP POST /production_days

Optional arguments: authorization, fieldsProductions, fieldsDivisions, fieldsAssignedproductiontaskcategories, fieldsProductiondays, include, body

Argument mapping:
• authorization → Authorization (header, optional) e.g. 54748d91aaf019c83c3c66edd2324fbb
• fieldsProductions → fields[productions] (query, optional) e.g. fields[productions]=name,divisions
• fieldsDivisions → fields[divisions] (query, optional) e.g. fields[divisions]=name
• fieldsAssignedproductiontaskcategories → fields[assignedProductionTaskCategories] (query, optional) e.g. fields[assignedProductionTaskCategories]=createdAt
• fieldsProductiondays → fields[productionDays] (query, optional) e.g. fields[productionDays]=workDate,measurement,isVisible,uniqueKey,options,custom,approvedAt,sentAt,sentStatus,categoryTotals,billedCompany,property,production,divisions,percentComplete
• include → include (query, optional) e.g. include=production,production.divisions,divisions,production.assignedProductionTaskCategories

