tools.description:
Creates a note attached to a production .

• The causer is derived from the Authorization token; clients must NOT send relationships.causer.
• attributes.description is REQUIRED for now and must be "note" .
• Use the production id (e.g., "1737315") in relationships.subject.data.id — do not send the UI Opportunity Number (e.g., "-1239").

